#====================
# Stenographer
# TODO:  finish typing and formatting this
#====================

Install Golang
https://golang.org/doc/install
$GOPATH will determine where Stenographer installs to!!!!!!!

Install Git
sudo apt-get install git

Download Stenographer
https://github.com/google/stenographer
go get github.com/google/stenographer (this will take a few minutes)
$GOPATH/go/bin/stenographer

Install Stenotype and Stenoread (jq) Dependencies
sudo apt-get install -y libaio-dev libleveldb-dev libsnappy-dev g++ libcap2-bin libseccomp-dev jq

Configure Stenotype
$GOPATH/go/src/github.com/google/stenographer/stenotype
make
(creates the stenotype binary, which has --help option)
